==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sirenical
<hw>Si*ren"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like, or
appropriate to, a siren; fascinating; deceptive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Here's couple of <qex>sirenical</qex> rascals shall enchant
ye.</q> <rj><qau>Marton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sirenize</ent>⟦br⟧
